
<div class='loginContent'>
  <a class='dismiss' href='#/'><img src='images/cross.png'></img></a>

  <div class='loginPane'>
    <h2>Already have Zooniverse username? Sign in here:</h2>
    <h3 class='flash'></h3>
    <form class='login'>
      <input name='username' placeholder='Username'></input>
      <input name='password' placeholder='Password' type='password'></input>
      
      <input type='submit' value='Sign In' name='signin'></input>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div  class='registerPane'> 
    <h2>Register for Cancer Research Project</h2>
    <form class='register'>

      <div class='innerLeft'> 
        <input name='First_Name' placeholder='First Name*' style="width:185px"></input>
        <input name='Last_Name' placeholder='Last Name*' style="width:185px"></input>
        <input name='Address_1' placeholder='Address 1*' style="width:374px"></input>
        <input name='Address_2' placeholder='Address 2*' style="width:256px"></input>
        <input name='telephone' placeholder='Telephone*' style="width:113px"></input>
        <input name='city' placeholder='City*' style="width: 185px" ></input>
        <input name='county' placeholder='County*' style="width: 67px"></input>
        <input name='postcode' placeholder='Postcode*' style="width:113px"></input>
        <p style= 'margin-top:0px'>* optional information</p>

        <p>Check here to agree to our <a target='blank' href='https://www.zooniverse.org/privacy'>privacy policy</a>  <input type='checkbox' style='display:inline' name='privacyOptIn' class='privacyOptIn' /></p>
        <p>We will not share your details with anyone else.</p>

        <p >Cancer Research UK would like to say a big thank you for participating in this research.  Cancer Research is the Worldâ€™s Leading Charity dedicated to saving lives through research.  We would like to keep in contact with you about upcoming news, events and fundraising activities.</p>

      </div>

      <div class='innerRight'>
        <input name='username' placeholder='Username'></input>
        <input name='Password' placeholder='Password' type='password'></input>
        <input name='Password_Confirmation' placeholder='Confirm Password' type='password'></input>
        <input name='Email' placeholder='Email'></input>
        <input type='submit' name='Register' value="Register"></input>
        <p style='font-size:11px; font-weight:600; margin;margin:0px; padding:0px'>If you are happy for your details to be shared with CR-UK and to receive this information using the email address you have provided, please tick this box:  <input type='checkbox' style='display:inline; position:relative; top: -22px; right :-184px' name='emailOptIn' class='emailOptIn' /> </p>

        <p style='font-size:11px; font-weight:600;margin:-20px 0px; padding:0px'>If you would prefer not to receive this information by post or phone, please tick this box: <input type='checkbox' style='display:inline; position:relative; top:-22px; right:-45px' name='mailPhoneOptOut' class='mailPhoneOptOut' /> </p>
       
      </div>
      
    </form>
  </div>

</div>